@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### 查询应用入口元信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/platform/app-entry/demo-app
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 开始应用登录（返回 app-login URL）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/platform/app-entry/demo-app/begin-login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "redirectUri": "/app-host/demo-app"
}

### 查询应用登录选项
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/platform/app-entry/demo-app/login-options
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
